---
import TransparentButton from "../buttons/TransparentButton.astro";
---

<main
  class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-5 lg:px-6 flex-grow min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-center"
>
  <section class="py-6 sm:py-8 md:py-10">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1
        class="font-heading text-4xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-[2.7rem] font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-900 to-slate-700 text-transparent bg-clip-text mb-3 md:mb-5 leading-tight"
      >
        Infrastructure That <span class="text-blue-600">Withstands Chaos</span>
      </h1>

      <h2
        class="font-sans text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl font-medium text-gray-600 mb-4 md:mb-5 leading-tight max-w-2xl"
      >
        AWS architecture engineered for mission-critical operations
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-3 mb-6 md:mb-8">
        <p
          class="font-sans text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed pl-3 border-l-2 sm:border-l-3 border-blue-500"
        >
          When downtime equals lost revenue, our systems maintain 100% uptime.
          <span
            class="block mt-1.5 text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium text-blue-600"
          >
            Crisis-proof deployments • Battle-tested designs • SLA-backed
            performance
          </span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col xs:flex-row gap-3 items-start">
        <TransparentButton
          href="https://cal.com/jrioscloud/45min"
          text="Get Crisis Prevention Audit"
          class="w-full xs:w-auto px-4 py-2.5 text-sm sm:text-base font-sans"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
